            "index": 2,
            "title": "Old Town",
            "subTitle": "Edinburgh - City Centre",
            "description": {
                "contentType": "hippostd:html",
                "value": "<p>Edinburgh&#39;s Old Town is part of a <vs-link type=\"external\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://www.ewht.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">UNESCO World Heritage Site</vs-link>, together with the Georgian era New Town on the north side of the city centre. The buildings you&#8217;ll see remain largely unchanged from how they would have looked centuries ago.</p>\n\n<p>The Old Town and Royal Mile is home to three filming locations from <em>Outlander</em>. If you&#8217;re looking for a memorable souvenir while you&#8217;re there, pop into <vs-link type=\"external\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://www.hamiltonandyoung.co.uk/\" title=\"Hamilton &#38; Young Jewellery Designers\" target=\"_blank\">Hamilton &#38; Young Jewellery Designers</vs-link> on the Royal Mile to browse Celtic and Outlander inspired items.</p>"
            },
